value.name: Store Analytics – Condition Monitoring
value.title: In-store Analytics – Condition Monitoring
value.description: Digitally connect and monitor your store environment to reduce operating costs and create experiences that customers love.

value.name: IoT Central Water Consumption application template
value.title: Water Consumption Monitoring
value.description: Enable remote tracking of water consumption to reduce field operations, detect leaks in time, while empowering cities to conserve water.

value.name: IoT Central Digital Distribution Center application template
value.title: Digital Distribution Center
value.description: Digitally manage warehouse conveyor belt system efficiency using object detection and tracking.

value.name: IoT Central Smart Inventory Management application template
value.title: Smart Inventory Management
value.description: Enable accurate inventory tracking and ensure shelves are always stocked.

value.name: IoT Central Connected Logistics application template
value.title: Connected Logistics
value.description: Track your shipment in real-time across air, water and land with location and condition monitoring.

value.name: IoT Central Smart Meter Analytics application template
value.title: Smart Meter Analytics
value.description: Connect utility meters to gain insights into billing, forecast consumption, and proactively detect outages.

value.name: IoT Central Micro-fulfillment Center
value.title: Micro-fulfillment Center
value.description: Digitally connect, monitor and manage all aspects of a fully automated fulfillment center to reduce costs by eliminating downtime while increasing security and overall efficiency.

value.name: IoT Central Continuous Patient Monitoring application template
value.title: Continuous Patient Monitoring
value.description: Connect and manage devices for in-patient and remote monitoring to improve patient outcomes, reduce re-admissions, and manage chronic diseases.

value.name: IoT Central PnP template (preview)
value.title: Custom application
value.description: Create an application with Azure IoT Plug and Play.

value.name: IoT Central Solar Power Monitoring application template
value.title: Solar Power Monitoring
value.description: Connect, monitor, and manage your solar panels and energy generation.

value.name: IoT Central Water Quality Monitoring application template
value.title: Water Quality Monitoring
value.description: Improve water quality and detect issues earlier by analyzing real-time measurements across your environment.

value.name: Store Analytics – Checkout
value.title: In-store Analytics – Checkout
value.description: Monitor and manage the checkout flow inside your store to improve efficiency and reduce wait times.

value.name: IoT Central Connected Waste Management application template
value.title: Connected Waste Management
value.description: Maximize efficiency in the collection of solid wastes by dispatching field operators at the right time along an optimized collection route.
